title: Le’Veon Bell Discussion & Week 11 Preview with Charles Davis
itunes:title: Le’Veon Bell Discussion & Week 11 Preview with Charles Davis
description:
DJ and Bucky discuss the Le’Veon Bell situation (0:30), preview all of the matchups on the Week 11 NFL slate (10:50). FOX Analyst Charles Davis joins the show to discuss the best that he has seen while broadcasting weekly this season (26:10), and close with Week 12 college football picks (41:35).
